1.description: Using Abilities grant you infinitely stacking <scaleBonus>Ability Haste</scaleBonus>.
1.name: AcceleratingSorcery
1.tooltip: Using an Ability grants <scaleBonus>@HastePerCast@ Ability Haste</scaleBonus>, stacking infinitely.

2.description:
Gain @ItemHaste@ Item Haste (equivalent to @TooltipCDR@% Item CDR).

Item Haste reduces the cooldown of all Item Abilities.
2.name: ApexInventor
2.tooltip:
Gain @ItemHaste@ Item Haste (equivalent to @TooltipCDR@% Item CDR).

Item Haste reduces the cooldown of all Item Abilities.

4.description: Gain increased damage, <scaleLevel>Damage</scaleLevel>, <healing>Healing</healing>, <shield>Shielding</shield>, and <scaleBonus>Ability Haste</scaleBonus>, but you <keywordMajor>cannot use your Ultimate Ability</keywordMajor>.
4.name: BacktoBasics
4.tooltip: Your Ultimate Ability is sealed. Gain @DamageAmp*100@% <scaleLevel>Damage</scaleLevel>, <healing>Healing</healing>, <shield>Shielding</shield>, and <scaleBonus>@Haste@ Ability Haste</scaleBonus>

5.description:
Gain the Banner of Command Summoner Spell.

Banner of Command empowers your ally for a brief duration.
5.name: BannerofCommand
5.tooltip: Your Partner gains a bonus @EmpowermentValue*100@% <scaleHealth>Health</scaleHealth>, <scaleAD>Attack Damage</scaleAD>, <scaleAP>Ability Power</scaleAP>, and <attackSpeed>Attack Speed</attackSpeed> for 10 seconds.

6.description:
Gain the Blade Waltz Summoner Spell.

Blade Waltz makes you untargetable while you dash at and damage enemies @TotalHits@ times.
6.name: BladeWaltz
6.tooltip: <rules>Makes you untargetable while you dash at and deal @Damage@ damage to enemies @TotalHits@ times (deals 50% on-hit damage).</rules>

8.description: Spawn a Battle Sled at the start of each combat.
8.name: BuckleUp
8.tooltip: Spawn a Battle Sled at the start of each combat.

9.description: You gain permanent Red and Blue Buffs.
9.name: BuffBuddies
9.tooltip: You gain permanent Red and Blue Buffs.

10.description: You enter combat launching from a cannon.
10.name: CannonFodder
10.tooltip: You enter combat launching from a cannon.

11.description: Casting your Ultimate also makes you <status>Invulnerable</status> for a short duration.
11.name: CantTouchThis
11.tooltip:
Casting your Ultimate also makes you <status>Invulnerable</status> for @InvulnDuration@s. 
@Cooldown@s cooldown.

12.description:
Gain the Castle Summoner Spell

Castle allows you to swap places with your ally.
12.name: Castle
12.tooltip:
Gain the Castle Summoner Spell

Allows you to swap places with your ally. You then gain @MSBuffAmount*100@% Move Speed for @MSBuffDuration@ seconds.

13.description: Gain <health>@Health@ Health</health>, but you deal @DamageReduction*100@% less damage.
13.name: CelestialBody
13.tooltip: Gain <health>@Health@ Health</health>, but you deal @DamageReduction*100@% less damage.

14.description: You are attached to your ally and can't move on your own. Your bonus movespeed is also granted to your ally, and you gain <scaleLevel>Ability Haste</scaleLevel> and <attackSpeed>Attack Speed</attackSpeed>.
14.name: Chauffeur
14.tooltip:
You are attached to your ally. Your bonus movespeed is also granted to your ally and you gain @Haste@ Ability Haste and @AttackSpeed*100@% Attack Speed.

Using a Dash or Blink ability removes the tether for 1.5s before snapping back to your ally.

15.description: <health>Healing</health> and Regen you do deals a portion of the value in <scaleAP>Magic Damage</scaleAP> to the nearest enemy champion.
15.name: CircleofDeath
15.tooltip: <health>Healing</health> and Regen you do deals <magicDamage>@HealToDamageConversion*100@% of that value in magic damage</magicDamage> to the nearest enemy champion.

16.description: Gain the <spellName>Electrocute</spellName> and <spellName>Phase Rush</spellName> Keystone Runes.
16.name: ComboMaster
16.tooltip: Gain the <spellName>Electrocute</spellName> and <spellName>Phase Rush</spellName> Keystone Runes.

17.description: Each round, mark an opponent to take @DamageAmp*100@% more damage and grant an extra @Gold@ gold on death.
17.name: ContractKiller
17.tooltip: Each round, mark an opposing champion. That champion takes @DamageAmp*100@% extra damage and grants an @Gold@ gold to you and your teammate when killed.

18.description: Gain a <shield>Shield</shield> scaling with max Health after <status>Immobilizing</status> an enemy champion.
18.name: CourageoftheColossus
18.tooltip: Gain <shield>@TotalShield@ max Health Shield</shield> after <status>Immobilizing</status> an enemy champion.

19.description: Your dash, leap, blink, or teleport Abilities gain <scaleLevel>@Haste@ Ability Haste</scaleLevel>.
19.name: Dashing
19.tooltip: Your dash, leap, blink, or teleport Abilities gain <scaleLevel>@Haste@ Ability Haste</scaleLevel>.

20.description: Upon dropping below @HealthThreshold*100@% Health, heal for @HealAmount*100@% max Health over 3 seconds.
20.name: DawnbringersResolve
20.tooltip: Upon dropping below @HealthThreshold*100@% Health, heal for @HealAmount*100@% max Health over 3 seconds.

21.description:
Gain the Defensive Maneuvers Summoner Spell

Defensive Maneuvers Casts both Summoner Barrier and Heal on you and your teammate.
21.name: DefensiveManeuvers
21.tooltip: Cast Summoner <abilityName>Barrier</abilityName> and <abilityName>Heal</abilityName> on you and your ally. Grants <shield>@BarrierAmount@ Shield</shield>, restores <healing>@HealAmount@ Health</healing>, and gives <speed>30% Move Speed</speed> for 1 second.

23.description: Gain the Fleet Footwork and Grasp of the Undying Keystone Runes.
23.name: DemonsDance
23.tooltip: Gain the <spellName>Fleet Footwork</spellName> and <spellName>Grasp of the Undying</spellName> Keystone Runes.

24.description:
Gain the Die Another Day Summoner Spell

Die Another Day creates a zone where no unit can die for 4 seconds.
24.name: DieAnotherDay
24.tooltip: Bless the ground under you for 4s, preventing any unit inside from falling below 10% of their max Health. At the end, units inside are healed for <healing>@HealFlatTooltip@ Health</healing>.

25.description: Your team's first death each round explodes, dealing massive damage.
25.name: DiveBomber
25.tooltip: Your team's first death each round explodes, dealing <trueDamage>@PercentMaxHPDamage*100@% of the targets max health as true damage</trueDamage> to nearby enemies.

26.description: Deal more damage to enemies the faster you are than them.
26.name: DontBlink
26.tooltip: Gain @BonusDamagePerMSDifference*1000@% bonus damage per <moveSpeed>10 Move Speed</moveSpeed> you have more than the target.

27.description: Your dash, leap, blink, or teleport Abilities leave behind a trail that detonates after 1 second.
27.name: Earthwake
27.tooltip: Your dash, leap, blink, or teleport Abilities leave behind a trail that detonates after 1 second, dealing @Damage@ physical damage.

28.description: Damaging enemies adds a stacking <scaleArmor>Armor</scaleArmor> and <scaleMR>Magic Resist</scaleMR> shred for @ShredDuration@s.
28.name: Erosion
28.tooltip:
Damaging enemies shreds @Shred*100@% Armor and Magic Resist for @ShredDuration@s.

Stacks up to @MaxStacks@ times.

29.description: Your Abilities apply on-hit effects. 1 second cooldown per target.
29.name: EtherealWeapon
29.tooltip: Your Abilities apply on-hit effects. 1 second cooldown per target.

30.description: Gain Ability Haste equal to <scaleAP>@APToHasteConversion*100@% of your Ability Power</scaleAP>
30.name: Eureka
30.tooltip: Gain Ability Haste equal to <scaleAP>@APToHasteConversion*100@% of your Ability Power</scaleAP>

31.description:
Gain the Evocation Summoner Spell

Evocation lets you channel to restore Health and Mana.
31.name: Evocation
31.tooltip: <rules> Lets you channel to restore <healing>Health</healing> and <scaleMana>Mana</scaleMana>. You then gain @MSBuffAmount*100@% Move Speed for @MSBuffDuration@ seconds.</rules>

32.description: Deal @BonusDamage*100@% more damage to enemies below @HealthThreshold*100@% health. Reset your basic abilities on takedown.
32.name: Executioner
32.tooltip: Deal @BonusDamage*100@% more damage to enemies below @HealthThreshold*100@% health. Reset your basic abilities on takedown.

33.tooltip: <keywordMajor>Automatically</keywordMajor> fire a Blitzcrank hook every 12 seconds at a nearby enemy champion.

34.description:
Start combat with a Black Shield for @ShieldDuration@s.

Black Shield blocks Magic Damage and Immobilizing effects.

34.tooltip:
Start combat with a Black Shield that blocks @ShieldAmount@ magic damage for @ShieldDuration@s.

Black Shield blocks Magic Damage and Immobilizing effects.

35.description:
Gain the Feel the Burn Summoner Spell.

Feel the Burn casts Ignite and Exhaust on all nearby enemy champions.
35.name: FeeltheBurn
35.tooltip: <rules>Casts <spellName>Ignite</spellName> and <spellName>Exhaust</spellName> on all nearby enemy champions.</rules>

36.description: Your Attacks apply an infinitely stacking <keywordMajor>Burn</keywordMajor>, dealing damage over time.
36.name: Firebrand
36.tooltip: Your Attacks also <keywordMajor>Burn</keywordMajor> enemies, dealing <scaleAP>@PercentMaxHPDamagePer5Seconds*20@% max Health Magic Damage</scaleAP> damage per second over @BleedDuration@ seconds. The <keywordMajor>Burn</keywordMajor> stacks infinitely.

38.description: Gain the <spellName>First Strike</spellName> and <spellName>Dark Harvest</spellName> Keystone Runes.
38.name: FromBeginningToEnd
38.tooltip: Gain the <spellName>First Strike</spellName> and <spellName>Dark Harvest</spellName> Keystone Runes.

39.description: Every @Cooldown@ seconds, Automatically Root nearby enemies for @RootDuration@ second.
39.name: FrostWraith
39.tooltip: Every @Cooldown@ seconds, <keywordMajor>Automatically</keywordMajor> <status>Root</status> nearby enemies for @RootDuration@ second.

40.description:
Gain the Frozen Foundations Summoner Spell

Frozen Foundations summons a wall of ice at a location.
40.name: FrozenFoundations
40.tooltip: <rules>Summon a wall of ice at target location.</rules>

43.description:
Gain the Now You See Me Summoner Spell

Now You See Me teleports you back to the starting position of your last Movement Ability.
43.name: NowYouSeeMe
43.tooltip:
Passive: Leave a mark behind whenever you use a Movement Ability.

Active: Return to the last mark you left. You then gain @MSBuffAmount*100@% Move Speed for @MSBuffDuration@ seconds.

44.description: Your <status>Slowing</status> effects reduce Move Speed by an extra 100.
44.name: IceCold
44.tooltip: Your <status>Slowing</status> effects reduce Move Speed by an extra 100.

45.description:
Your Abilities apply a stacking Burn, dealing Magic Damage over time.

Your Burn effects reduce your basic Ability cooldowns.
45.name: InfernalConduit
45.tooltip:
Your Abilities apply a stacking Burn, dealing @BleedDamageTooltip@ Magic Damage per second for @BleedDuration@ seconds. The Burn stacks infinitely.

All your Burn effects lower your remaining Basic Ability Cooldowns by @FlatCooldownRefundPerTick@s when they damage enemies.

46.description: You gain the Infernal Soul, dealing bonus damage when you hit enemies with Abilities or Attacks.
46.name: InfernalSoul
46.tooltip: You gain the Infernal Soul, dealing bonus damage when you hit enemies with Abilities or Attacks.

48.description: Your Abilities can Critically Strike. Gain 20% Crit Chance.

48.tooltip: Your Abilities can Critically Strike for 140% total damage. Gain 20% Crit Chance. Gain an additional @APToCritConversion@ Crit Chance scaling with your AP.

49.description: Each round, you and your teammate get an additional Juice for free.

49.tooltip: Each round, you and your teammate get an additional Juice for free.

50.description: Gain the <spellName>Summon Aery</spellName> and <spellName>Arcane Comet</spellName> Keystone Runes.
50.name: KeystoneConjurer
50.tooltip: Gain the <spellName>Summon Aery</spellName> and <spellName>Arcane Comet</spellName> Keystone Runes.

51.name: LightemUp
51.tooltip: Every 4th Attack deals additional <scaleMagic>@Damage@ magic damage</scaleMagic>.

52.description: Gain <scaleAD>Attack Damage</scaleAD> scaling with your <attackSpeed>Attack Speed</attackSpeed>.

52.tooltip: Gain <scaleAD>@ASToADConversion*.1@ Attack Damage</scaleAD> per <attackSpeed>0.1 Attack Speed</attackSpeed>.

53.description: On Round start you grow large (<scaleAD>Adaptive Force</scaleAD> and <healing>Health</healing>) or tiny (<scaleLevel>Ability Haste</scaleLevel> and <speed>Move Speed</speed>).

53.tooltip: On Round start you grow large, gaining (<scaleAD>@ADAmp*100@% Adaptive Force</scaleAD> and <healing>@HealthAmp*100@% Health</healing>) or tiny (<scaleLevel>@Haste@ Ability Haste</scaleLevel> and <speed>@MovespeedAmp*100@% Move Speed</speed>).

54.description: Your Attacks grant you stacking <scaleAP>Ability Power</scaleAP> and your Abilities grant you <scaleAD>Attack Damage</scaleAD>.
54.name: MasterofDuality
54.tooltip: Your Attacks grant you <scaleAP>@APGained@ Ability Power</scaleAP> and your Abilities grant you <scaleAD>@ADGained@ Attack Damage</scaleAD>, stacking infinitely until the end of the round.

55.tooltip:
Automatically throw a lantern to your ally every 12 seconds.

The lantern can be clicked to dash to you.

56.description: Increase <healing>max Health</healing> by half of your <scaleMana>Mana</scaleMana>.

56.tooltip: Increase <healing>max Health</healing> by half of your <scaleMana>Mana</scaleMana>.

57.description: You gain the Mountain Soul, gaining <shield>Shield</shield> after being out of combat for a short time.
57.name: MountainSoul
57.tooltip: You gain the Mountain Soul, gaining <shield>Shield</shield> after being out of combat for a short time.

58.description: Your Attacks reduce your cooldowns by @CooldownRefund@ second.

58.tooltip: Your Attacks reduce your cooldowns by @CooldownRefund@ second.

59.description: You can buy any number of Mythic Items.
59.name: Mythical
59.tooltip: You can buy any number of Mythic Items.

60.description: Gain the Ocean Soul, granting high <healing>Health</healing> and <scaleMana>Mana</scaleMana> regen after damaging enemies.
60.name: OceanSoul
60.tooltip: Gain the Ocean Soul, granting high <healing>Health</healing> and <scaleMana>Mana</scaleMana> regen after damaging enemies.

61.description: <keywordMajor>Automatically</keywordMajor> fire a boomerang at a nearby enemy every 7s.
61.name: OkBoomerang
61.tooltip: <keywordMajor>Automatically</keywordMajor> fire a boomerang at a nearby enemy every 7s, dealing @Damage@ adaptive damage to enemies hit.

63.description:
After using a dash, leap, blink, or teleport Ability you gain @ResistsPerStack@ Armor and Magic Resist.

This stacks up to @MaxStacks@ times.
63.name: OutlawsGrit
63.tooltip:
After using a dash, leap, blink, or teleport Ability you gain @ResistsPerStack@ Armor and Magic Resist.

This stacks up to @MaxStacks@ times.

64.description: Gain hugely increased <healing>Health Regen</healing>, which is further increased while low on Health.
64.name: Perseverance
64.tooltip: Gain <healing>@BaseRegen*100@% base Health Regen</healing>, increased to <healing>@AmpedRegen*100@% base Health Regen</healing> while below 25% Health.

65.tooltip:
Permanently gain 1 Ability Power when you hit enemies with Abilities.

1 second cooldown.

AP Gained: @f1@

66.description:
Automatically slash in a circle around you, dealing bonus damage on the outer edge every 15 seconds.

Your Automatic Augments are affected by Ability Haste.

Automatically slash in a circle around you, dealing bonus damage on the outer edge every 15 seconds.

Your Automatic Augments are affected by Ability Haste.

69.tooltip: On dropping below @HealthThreshold1*100@ or @HealthThreshold2*100@% Health, nearby enemies are <status>Knocked Back</status>.

70.description: You constantly <healing>heal</healing> while moving, increased by distance travelled.
70.name: RestlessRestoration
70.tooltip: You heal for @HealCalcPer1000Units@ per 1000 distance traveled.

71.description: Gain @MeleeRangeIncrease@ Attack Range, reduced to @RangedRangeIncrease@ for ranged characters.
71.name: ScopedWeapons
71.tooltip: Gain @MeleeRangeIncrease@ Attack Range, reduced to @RangedRangeIncrease@ for ranged characters.

72.description: Your Abilities mark enemies, causing them to take extra damage from your ally's next effect.
72.name: SearingDawn
72.tooltip: Your Abilities mark enemies, causing them to take an additional <magicDamage>@Damage@ magic damage</magicDamage> from your ally's next Attack or Ability.

73.description: After using a dash, leap, blink, or teleport Ability or exiting <stealth>Stealth</stealth>, gain @MSAmount@ Move Speed for @BuffDuration@ seconds.
73.name: ShadowRunner
73.tooltip: After using a dash, leap, blink, or teleport Ability or exiting <stealth>Stealth</stealth>, gain @MSAmount@ Move Speed for @BuffDuration@ seconds.

74.description: Your Attacks reduce an enemy's damage by @DamageReduction*100@% for 3 seconds.
74.name: ShrinkRay
74.tooltip: Your Attacks reduce an enemy's damage by @DamageReduction*100@% for 3 seconds.

75.description: Every second, apply a stacking <keywordMajor>Burn</keywordMajor> to nearby enemy champions scaling with your <health>Max Health</health>. The <keywordMajor>Burn</keywordMajor> stacks infinitely.

75.tooltip: Every second, apply a stacking <keywordMajor>Burn</keywordMajor>, dealing <health>@BleedDamageTooltip@ per second as <scaleAP>Magic Damage</scaleAP> for @BleedDuration@ seconds</health> to enemy champions within @Range@ range. The <keywordMajor>Burn</keywordMajor> stacks infinitely.

78.description: 40% of damage dealt to your ally is redirected to you, and 40% of <healing>healing</healing> they recieve is given to you as well.

78.tooltip: 40% of damage dealt to your ally is redirected to you, and 40% of <healing>healing</healing> they recieve is given to you as well.

79.description: Gain the <spellName>Lethal Tempo</spellName> and <spellName>Conqueror</spellName> Keystone Runes.
79.name: SymphonyofWar
79.tooltip: Gain the <spellName>Lethal Tempo</spellName> and <spellName>Conqueror</spellName> Keystone Runes.

80.description: You can <crit>Critically Defend</crit> using your Crit Chance (max @MaxChance*100@% chance), giving you a chance to reduce damage. Gain @CritChance*100@% Crit Chance.
80.name: TankItOrLeaveIt
80.tooltip: You can <crit>Critically Defend</crit> using your Crit Chance (max @MaxChance*100@% chance), giving you a chance to reduce damage taken by @DamageReduction*100@%. Gain @CritChance*100@% Crit Chance.

81.description: Your Attacks grant you <moveSpeed>@MSPerHit@ Move Speed</moveSpeed>, stacking infinitely. Gain AS equal to @MSToASConversion*10000@% of your MS.
81.name: TapDancer
81.tooltip: Your Attacks grant you <moveSpeed>@MSPerHit@ Move Speed</moveSpeed>, stacking infinitely. Gain AS equal to @MSToASConversion*10000@% of your MS.

82.description: Gain <scaleAD>@AD@ Attack Damage</scaleAD>, <scaleLevel>@AbilityHaste@ Ability Haste</scaleLevel>, and <scaleAD>@Lethality@ Lethality</scaleAD>.
82.name: TheBrutalizer
82.tooltip: Gain <scaleAD>@AD@ Attack Damage</scaleAD>, <scaleLevel>@AbilityHaste@ Ability Haste</scaleLevel>, and <scaleAD>@Lethality@ Lethality</scaleAD>.

83.description: Remove your current items, gain random items each combat instead. Bonus stats and item damage is increased by @ItemStatAmp*100@%.
83.name: ThiefsGloves
83.tooltip: Remove your current items, gain random items each combat instead. Bonus stats and item damage is increased by @ItemStatAmp*100@%.

85.description: <status>Immobilizing</status> enemy champions applies a <keywordMajor>Burn</keywordMajor> that deals damage over time, stacking infinitely.
85.name: Tormentor
85.tooltip: <status>Immobilizing</status> enemy champions applies a <keywordMajor>Burn</keywordMajor>, dealing <scaleAP>@PercentMaxHPDamagePer5Seconds*20@% max Health Magic Damage</scaleAP> per second for @BleedDuration@ seconds. The <keywordMajor>Burn</keywordMajor> stacks infinitely.

86.description: When you damage a champion from far away, <keywordMajor>automatically</keywordMajor> fire a <abilityName>Trueshot Barrage</abilityName> at them.
86.name: TrueshotProdigy
86.tooltip: When you damage someone from over @SnipeDistance@ units away, <keywordMajor>automatically</keywordMajor> fire a <abilityName>Trueshot Barrage</abilityName> at them, dealing @Damage@ damage at global range. @Cooldown@s cooldown.

87.description: Your Attacks fire a bolt at an additional target dealing reduced damage and applying on-hits.
87.name: Typhoon
87.tooltip: Your Attacks fire a bolt at an additional target dealing @ADRatio*100@% damage and applying on-hits.

88.description: Once per round, refresh your Ultimate Ability after casting it.
88.name: UltimateRevolution
88.tooltip: Once per round, refresh your Ultimate Ability after casting it.

89.name: Vanish
89.tooltip:
Become Invisible for @StealthDuration@ seconds or until you Attack or use an Ability.
This stealth cannot be revealed by the Arcane Sweeper trinket.

90.description: Gain massively increased damage and Omnivamp while your partner is dead.
90.name: Vengeance
90.tooltip: Gain @DamageAmp*100@% increased damage and @Omnivamp*100@% Omnivamp while your partner is dead.

91.description: Your <healing>Heals</healing> grant extra <shield>Shield</shield> and your <shield>Shields</shield> grant extra <healing>Healing</healing>.
91.name: VirtuousCycle
91.tooltip: Your <healing>Heals</healing> grans an extra <shield>@ShieldFromHealPercentage*100@% Shield</shield> and your <shield>Shields</shield> grant an extra <healing>@HealFromShieldPercentage@% Healing</healing>.

92.description: Your Item and damage over time effects can Critically Strike. Gain @CritChance*100@% Crit chance.

92.tooltip: Your Item and damage over time effects can Critically Strike for @CritDamage*100@% extra damage. Gain 20% Crit chance.

93.description:

Warmup Routine allows you to channel to increase your damage for the rest of the round.
93.name: WarmupRoutine
93.tooltip: Channel to increase your damage by 2% per second, up to 24% max.

94.tooltip: When your ally drops below <health>@AllyHealthThreshold*100@% Health</health>, trade <health>@CurrentHealthToDrain*100@% of your current Health</health> for that much <shield>Shield</shield> on your ally.

95.description: Your <healing>Healing</healing> and <shield>Shielding</shield> also increases the target's <scaleArmor>Armor</scaleArmor> and <scaleMR>Magic Resist</scaleMR> for 3 seconds.
95.name: WindspeakersBlessing
95.tooltip: Your <healing>Healing</healing> and <shield>Shielding</shield> also increases the target's <scaleArmor>Armor</scaleArmor> and <scaleMR>Magic Resist</scaleMR> by @Resists@ for 3 seconds.

96.description: Gain 1 level now, and 1 bonus level every other round. Your level cap is removed.
96.name: WisdomofAges
96.tooltip: Gain 1 level now, and 1 bonus level every other round. Your level cap is removed.

98.description: Gain <moveSpeed>Move Speed</moveSpeed> equal to double your <scaleLevel>Ability Haste</scaleLevel>.
98.name: WithHaste
98.tooltip: Gain <moveSpeed>Move Speed</moveSpeed> equal to double your <scaleLevel>Ability Haste</scaleLevel>.

99.description:
Gain the Zhonya's Epiphany Summoner Spell.

Zhonya's Epiphany puts you in Stasis for 3 seconds, rendering you Untargetable and Invulnerable for the duration but also unable to act, and resetting your basic ability cooldowns.
99.name: ZhonyasEpiphany
99.tooltip: Puts you in Stasis for 3 seconds, rendering you Untargetable and Invulnerable for the duration but also unable to act, and resetting your basic ability cooldowns.
